  "prompt": "Which is best online shopping site in india for bags?",
  "response": "There are several popular online shopping sites in India where you can find a wide variety of bags. Here are some of the best options:\n\n1. **Amazon India**: Offers a vast collection of bags from various brands, including backpacks, handbags, and luggage, with detailed reviews and competitive prices.\n\n2. **Flipkart**: Another major e-commerce platform in India, Flipkart features a wide range of bags and often has great discounts and offers.\n\n3. **Myntra**: Known primarily for fashion, Myntra has a good selection of trendy bags, including purses and backpacks from popular brands.\n\n4. **Ajio**: An Indian fashion and lifestyle e-commerce platform that offers a variety of stylish bags. They often feature unique designs.\n\n5. **Snapdeal**: This site provides a variety of bags at affordable prices, including casual and formal options.\n\n6. **Paytm Mall**: Along with various electronics and home goods, Paytm Mall offers bags from different brands, sometimes with cashback offers.\n\n7. **ShopClues**: Known for discount shopping, it has a wide range of bags at competitive prices.\n\nWhen choosing an online shopping site, consider factors like product variety, prices, discounts, return policies, and customer reviews to find the best option for your needs.",
